    schema1:description "Currently Risk Director at Legal & General, Simon served as Chief Risk Officer (CRO) for LGIM, the UK’s largest fund manager, and for the past 6 years as CRO of L&G Capital, overseeing housing and regeneration businesses. His remit included major housing areas such as L&G Modular Housing, Build-to-Rent, Affordable Housing, Cala Homes, Strategic Land, together with urban regeneration, clean energy, and venture businesses. He was a key member or advisor across all relevant boards, committees, and governance structures."@en ;
